President Donald J. Trump has announced his intent to appoint several individuals to be Members of the President's Advisory 1776 Commission. The appointed individuals include Larry Arnn, who will serve as Chair, and Dr. Carol M. Swain, who will serve as Vice Chair. Other appointees include Brooke L. Rollins, Vincent M. Haley, Victor Davis Hanson, Phil Bryant, Mike Gonzalez, John Gibbs, Scott McNealy, Gay Hart Gaines, Ned Ryun, Charles Kirk, Peter N. Kirsanow, Charles R. Kesler, Dr. Thomas K. Lindsay, Jerry C. Davis, Michael Farris, and Bob McEwen. The terms for these appointments will be for two years.